  Hit chan5 su7-kiaN7 ti7 Tai5-oan5 sou2 tu2-tioh8 choe7-choe7 pi3-bit8 su7-kiaN7 e5 tiong-kan thang kong2 si7 tian2-heng5-tek--e5. Ti7 chian3-cheng tiong, Jit8-pun2 chai7 Tai5-oan5 e5 thong2-ti7-chia2 u7 chiap-soa3 ap-pek hiah-e5 chu7-bin5 bo5 soah; put-koan2 in si7 han3-jin5 a2-si7 ko-san-chok8. Chian3-cheng e5 kiok8-se3 chit8-e7 bai2, seng3-li7 e5 ng3-bang7 chit8-e7 bo5--khi3 e5 si5, in e5 ap-pek chiu7 oat8-ju2 ke-thiN in e5 chan5-jim2-seng3. Tng lian5-hap8-kun khek-hok8 Thai3-peng5-iuN5 e5 to2-su7, thau2-pang3 hia e5 goan5 chu7-bin5 e5 si5, Jit8-pun2 lang5 chiu7 oat8-ju2 kiaN-hiaN5 koh kiong5-pou7, in-ui7 lian5-hap8-kun chiam7-chiam7 u7 kho2-leng5-seng3 thang lai5 Tai5-oan5 chiuN7-liok8. In siuN7 kong2 Tai5-oan5 lang5 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 si7 ti7 am3-chiN7 e5 tiong-kan teh tong5-cheng5 lian5-hap8-kun--e5, sou2-i2 ban7-it na7 chiuN7-liok8 e5 si5, oe7 khi3 pang-chan7 in. Ui7-tioh8 an2-ni, Jit8-pun2 e5 keng2-chhat chiu7 kang2-kiu3 ban7-choan5 e5 tui3-chhek, beh chiong sou2 u7 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 chip8-tiong cho3-hoe2; iau3-kin2 e5 si5-ki na7 kau3, beh chong2 chau5-biat8 in. Tai5-oan5 chiah che7 e5 jin5-khau2 si7 tui3 chha-put-to 600 ban7 e5 han3-chok8 e5 Tai5-oan5 lang5 lai5 chou-seng5--e5. Ia7 chiah-e5 lang5 si7 khia7-khi2 ti7 sai-pou7 e5 piN5-iuN5, chiu7-si7 hit e5 tui3 pak-peng5 tit8-thau3 kau3 lam5-peng5--e5. Ti7-chiah-e5 Tai5-oan5 lang5 e5 tiong-kan u7 saN-ban7 lang5 i2-siong7 si7 i2-keng nia2 se2-le2 e5 Ki-tok-tou5. In si7 chin7-tiong--e5, na7 m7-si7 chin7-tiong--e5 lai5 kong2, choe3-chio2 iah8 si7 kui-sun7--e5. Chiah-e5 lang5 chai7 Jit8-pun2 e5 tong-kiok8-chia2 lai5 khoaN3, si7 bo5 sim2-mih8 toa7 bun7-te5. M7-ku2 ti7 tiong-iong e5 soaN-meh8, i2-kip8 tang hai2-hoaN7 u7 goan5-si2 bin5-chok8 khia7-khi2 ti7-hia; in e5 siau3-giah8 iok-liok8 15 ban7, in e5 seng3-chit oan5-choan5 si7 koh-iuN7--e5. Chiah-e5 goan5-si2 bin5-chok8 chiam7-chiam7 teh hou7 hiah-e5 koan2 in e5 Jit8-pun2 keng2-chhat thau5-khak khi2 toa7 thiaN3. In si7 chhin-chhiuN7 Bou7-ni5-o3 e5 Lai5-khek-chok8, iau2