  1895 ni5, te7-it chhu3 Tiong Jit8 chian3-cheng au7, kun-ku3 Ma2-koan tiau5-iok e5 tiau5-kiaN7, Tiong-kok siu7 pek, kou-put-chiong tioh8 chiong Tai5-oan5 jiong7-tou7 hou7 Jit8-pun2. Chong2-si7 Tai5-oan5 e5 peh-siN3 ku7-choat8, m7 seng5-jin7 chit e5 tiau5-iok; chiu7 soan-pou3 Tai5-oan5 cho3 tok8-lip8 e5 kiong7-ho5 kok. Ui7-tioh8 an2-ni, Jit8-pun2 e5 hai2-kun chiu7 chek-si5 tui3 pak-pou7 siong7-liok8, hit e5 te7-hng cheng3-koan5 chiu7 ti7 iu-se3 e5 bu2-lek8 e5 bin7-cheng5 liam5-piN khui-hoe khi3. Chi2-u7 koan5-soaN e5 goan5 chu7-bin5 u7 ho2-taN2 kap i ti2-khong3, ke3-siok8 kap i chian3 kui2-na7 ni5. Khi2-chhou Jit8-pun2 lang5 chin bo5 eng5, mi5-jit8 eng7 sim ti7 siat lut8-le7 kap hoat-leng7, thang lai5 ti7-li2 hiah-e5 khia7-khi2 ti7 sai-pou7 piN5-iuN5 e5 Tai5-oan5 lang5; chiu7 bo5 sim-chiaN5 thang koan2-kou3 soaN-te7, i2-kip8 kai2-koat hiah-e5 chhu2 lang5-thau5-khak--e5. Kau3 in he7 kha-chhiu2 chou2-chit tho2-hoat8-tui7 beh khi3 tho2-hoat8 in e5 si5, chiah chai-iaN2 beh cheng-hok8 in m7-si7 iong5-iN7, u7 i3-goa7 e5 hi-seng kap kan-lan5 ti7-teh. In e5 iu5-kek-tui7 bih ti7 am7 e5 chhiu7-na5 lai7, i2-kip8 chhim e5 soaN-giam5-nih, ti7-chia ti7-hia thau phah Jit8-pun2 kun, hou7 in lap8 liau2 tang7-tang7 e5 hiat-soe3. Chiah-e5 lang5 chu7-jian5 si7 chin m7 hoaN-hi2 jim7-ho5 e5 bu2-chong pou7-tui7 lai5 chhim-liok8 in e5 soaN-che7; in-ui7 in liah8 hiah-e5 soaN-che7 cho3 si7 in e5 tek8-iu2 chai5-san2. In siong5-siong5 khoaN3 hiah-e5 khia7-khi2 ti7 piN5-iuN5 e5 Tai5-oan5 lang5 si7 lau3-sai2-be2--e5, in-ui7 tu3 bo5 saN-e7 pou2-thau5 chiu7 liam5-piN un--loh8-khi3. Tok8-tok8 in chiah si7 ai3-houN3 chu7-iu5 e5 koan5-soaN teng2 e5 chu7-bin5, iah8 chiu3-choa7 m7 tau5-hang5. 
  Iu5-kek chian3 ke3-siok8 chap8 ni5 ku2, ti7 hit e5 khun3-lan5 e5 soaN-te7-nih, u7-si5 thai5, u7-si5 hioh; au7-lai5 hit e5 chong-pi7 iu-siu3 e5 Jit8-pun2-kun u7 chiam7-chiam7 tit8-tioh8 iu2-li7 e5 te7-pou7. Jit8-pun2 lang5 ui7-tioh8 koaN2-kin2 beh ti7 ko-san-chok8 e5 te7-kai3 lai5 chhai2-hoat8 chiuN-lo2 soaN i2-kip8 kiN5-thaN choe7-choe7 po2-kui3 e5 bok8-chhai5. Chiu7 chun2-pi7 beh kap chiah-e5 u7 ke3-tat8 e5 tek8-jin5¢wThai3-ia5-chok8, Bu2-lun2-chok8, i2-kip8 Pai5-oan-chok8¢wlai5 teng3-lip8 chit8 e5 bo5 sit the2-bian7 e5 ho5-iok. Jit8-pun2-kun kap chiah-e5 hoan-sia7 teh chian3 e5 si5, cham2-jian5 u7 hi-seng, u7 sit-loh8 kui2-na7 e5 pou7-tui7. Chiu7 chiong ko-san-chok8 e5 iau3-sai3 eng7 tian7-soaN3 ka7 i ui5--khi2-lai5, pang3 hou7 in khi3 kou-lip8. 
  In e5 boat8-lou7 si7 boe7 bian2-tit e5. Hoan-sia7 chit8-sia7 koe3 chit8-sia7 tit8-tit8 hang5--khi3, soa3 kap in kang2-ho5; chi2-u7 chhun chit8 ui7 iong2-beng2 e5 Thai3-lou2-kok sia7 (Thai3-ia5 chok8 e5 chit8 sia7) kian-siu2 m7-goan5 hang5. In e5 tin7-te7 si7 siat ti7 Thai3-lou2-kok soaN-giam5 teng2 hiam2-iau3 e5 chioh8-tong7-nih, in u7 chiam3-ku3 chit8 jiah thian-jian5 e5 chhiu7-na5, si7 Jit8-pun2 kun bo5 hoat-tou7 thang sip8-kek e5; sui-bong2 si7 an2-ni, in kau3 be2 iah8 si7 tioh8 hang5, na7 bo5 chiu7 go7-si2. Au7-lai5 jit8-chi2 i2-keng kau3, Thai3-ia5 chok8 e5 thau5-lang5 chiu7 kam2-kak tioh8 kong2 in e5 khui3-lat8 i2-keng chhiong-hun tit-tioh8 cheng3-beng5 lah, na7 ke3-siok8 koh thai5 loh8-khi3, an2-ni sng3 m7-si7 chhong-beng5; siuN7 kong2 ti7 hit e5 si5-chun7 lai5 kang2-ho5 iah8 i2-keng m7-si7 kian3-siau3 e5 su7 lah. In-ui7 ¡§U7-si5 thang thai5-lang5, u7-si5 thang i-ti7, u7-si5 thang kau-chian3, u7-si5 thang ho5-ho2.¡¨ Kiam2 bo5 sim2-mih8 ta-pou-lang5 a2-si7 hu7-jin5-lang5 thang ui7-tioh8 in lai5 kap tui3-tek8 teng3-lip8 chit8 e5 kong-eng5 e5 ho5-iok mah? Chi7-chui7 beh chhut-thau5 lai5 tam-tng in e5 thong-ek8 i2-kip8 tiau-kai2-chia2 e5 chit-bu7 ah? Chiong3-gi7 it koat, chiu7 tui3 in ka-ki7 e5 peh-siN3 e5 tiong-kan soan2-chhut chit8 ui7 hu7-jin5-lang5 kio3 cho3 Chi-oang2, si7 36 hoe3 lang5. I bat kap chit8 e5 Tai5-oan5 e5 seng-li2 lang5 kiat-hun, ia7 khia7-khi2 ti7 tang-hai2-hoaN7 e5 Hoe-lian5-kang2. I bat Jit8-pun2 oe7, iah8 oe7 kong2 chin liu5-li7 e5 Tai5-oan5 oe7 kah na2 chhin-chhiuN7 kong2 in ka-ki7 e5 Thai3-ia5 oe7 chit8-iuN7. Tui3 pat8 hong-bin7 lai5 kong2, i ia7 si7 chit8 ui7 phoaN3-toan3-lek8 kian7-choan5 e5 ti3-sek hu7-lu2, chin u7 koan-sim ti7 i e5 tong5-pau e5 li7-hai7 koan-he7. Tui3 i e5 gau5 chiu-soan5, ti7 Jit8-pun2 kun kap Thai3-ia5-chok8 e5 tiong-kan ko2-jian5 seng5-lip8 liau2 chit8 e5 liong2-hong moa2-i3 e5 ho5-iok. Tui3 hit-tiap8 i2-au7, Chi-oang2 chit e5 mia5-ji7 chiu7 tauh8-tauh8 hou7 lang5 khoaN3 chin u7 khi2. Jit8-pun2 e5 tong-kiok8-chia2